title: Apple iOS 9: It’s coming on September 16 with deep 3D Touch integration for new iPhones
text: Apple will release iOS 9, the next version of its mobile operating system, on September 16. It has revealed the all the details about the new features it will contain, including how it will work with 3D Touch. Here's what you need to know. »
